Swajas Air Plans to Raise 375 Million Rupees in Initial Offer

-- B y   P a r e s h   J a t a k i a
-- 
2011-09-22T05:15:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/swajas-air-plans-to-raise-375-million-rupees-in-initial-offer.html
Swajas Air Charters Ltd. plans to
raise as much as 375 million rupees ($7.7 million) selling
shares in an initial public offer, according to an advertisement
in the Business Standard newspaper today.  The Chennai-based air-charter services provider aims to
sell shares at 90 rupees to 100 rupees each from Sept. 26 to
Sept. 28, the advertisement showed.  Aryaman Financial Services
Ltd. (AMFS)  will manage the share sale.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Paresh Jatakia in Mumbai at 
 pareshj@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Niveditha Ravi at 
 nravi2@bloomberg.net  